---
title: Goat Cheese Chicken with Figgy Balsamic with Garlic Roasted Carrots & Asparagus
description: How are we going to make chicken special tonight? Say it with us now, all together: PAN SAUCE! When you combine luscious fig jam with tart balsamic vinegar and a little of the magic ingredient (butter), it truly becomes something more than the sum of its parts. Add a layer of tangy melted goat cheese on top, serve with a side of garlicky roasted potatoes and carrots, and you’ve got a quick, delicious way to elevate this weeknight dinner idea.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/goat-cheese-chicken-with-figgy-balsamic-6cd3db59.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/goat-cheese-chicken-with-figgy-balsamic-63ed139c8f0b13a4b30afec3-555da53e.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/goat-cheese-chicken-with-figgy-balsamic-63ed139c8f0b13a4b30afec3
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
cuisine: Mediterranean
